{"tid":754372,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大dodo老母麵悼念區","createTime":"2018-07-24T11:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T06:43:02.000Z","uid":22845,"like":165,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"70f323cddac83cf0023eea1143561571c48bb83f","tid":754372,"uid":22845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:03:16.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>天妒英才</strong></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"http://pic25.nipic.com/20121208/5243356_141406332341_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic25.nipic.com%2F20121208%2F5243356_141406332341_2.jpg&h=798ee36c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/190105_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F190105_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ff1d52ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一代英雄，帶領一眾貼經台巴打出生入死，經歷無數次貼倉死老豆，由佢大筆一揮，畫圖指揮左牛兵右熊將，大軍盡在彈指之間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成功避過丁圖一劫，技驚四座，召喚貼經台巴打團結對抗大戶，勁假時段力保不失，功德無量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可惜終遇滑鐵盧，被雷軍所害，敗於屌米，最終榴槤爆春袋，從此音訊全無、死無全屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\\|/ 大家請珍惜麵麵 \\|/</div>"},{"pid":"8cd7dd06af3d599f9cd6c859deceb74c5244cea9","tid":754372,"uid":22845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> \\|/"},{"pid":"000d1abc3047b1c491611f48fb5be7f61f13939c","tid":754372,"uid":412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:06:57.000Z","msg":"\\|/"},{"pid":"6c723f11d9d7b3097c367144db750f807ddde19e","tid":754372,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c952b6ec6adf2ad104e57e4e8a1e69d14221f79","tid":754372,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:12:01.000Z","msg":"睇黎老母面應該係春袋爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad7651a6978af777035b1d38bdecda100490cbe","tid":754372,"uid":22845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:14:43.000Z","msg":"返來囉～"},{"pid":"014118d3e338e8465f913e8624163bb14b6a9814","tid":754372,"uid":37278,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:15:58.000Z","msg":"其實大dodo咁耐以黎賺多定蝕多"},{"pid":"b086864efa26e94a3562e2b09f3a44b6f9089ae8","tid":754372,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260ee36bb20b5693bfccca79e959200a4d197547","tid":754372,"uid":10922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"麵麵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n\\|/<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3624991b4e4e0cc468e4ccace25c6aeda25772","tid":754372,"uid":29246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T11:18:32.000Z","msg":"rip p.s. 不過自從無咗佢之後,個市好似好咗好多"},{"pid":"83668ef980882c15b7e2b811f0e55275d058c620","tid":754372,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"014118d3e338e8465f913e8624163bb14b6a9814","tid":754372,"uid":37